OL,3,CTwo pupils hurt after falling from
OL,4,Cmoving bus window
OL,6,FWatch the moment school students in a
OL,7,Fplay-fight on the upper level of a
OL,8,Fmoving bus fell out of the window
OL,10,FTwo school students have been taken to
OL,11,Fhospital after falling from the window
OL,12,Fof a moving bus in Walsall.
OL,14,FThe incident was captured on
OL,15,Feyewitness video, which shows the boys
OL,16,Fplay-fighting at the back of the upper
OL,17,Fdeck as the bus travelled home from
OL,18,Fschool.
