OL,3,CTwo pupils hurt after falling from
OL,4,Cmoving bus window
OL,6,FThe footage shows the moment the
OL,7,Fwindow gives way as the boys fall
OL,8,Fbackwards against it, before both
OL,9,Ftopple out of the bus and onto the
OL,10,Froad.
OL,12,FA fellow passenger can be heard
OL,13,Fshouting: "Oh no".
OL,15,FEmergency services were called to
OL,16,FSutton Road at around 3.30pm on 2
OL,17,FFebruary.
