OL,3,CTwo pupils hurt after falling from
OL,4,Cmoving bus window
OL,6,FThe youngsters were taken to Walsall
OL,7,FManor Hospital with injuries deemed
OL,8,F"potentially serious", but 'not life-
OL,9,Fchanging".
OL,11,FA West Midlands Police spokesperson
OL,12,Fsaid the schoolchildren were taken to
OL,13,Fhospital.
OL,15,FIn a statement they said: "We were
OL,16,Fcalled to Sutton Road, Walsall, just
OL,17,Fbefore 3.30pm yesterday after two boys
OL,18,Ffell from the window of a moving bus.
