OL,6,F"The boys were taken to the hospital
OL,7,Fwith injuries that are thankfully not
OL,8,Fbelieved to be life-changing.
OL,10,F"We have spoken to a number of
OL,11,Fwitnesses and have been liaising with
OL,12,Fthe bus company."
OL,14,FA West Midlands Ambulance Service
OL,15,Fspokesperson said: "We were called to
OL,16,Fan incident on Beacon Road in Aldridge
OL,17,Fat around 3.30pm and sent two
OL,18,Fambulances and a paramedic officer to
OL,19,Fthe scene.
